{"tid":38348,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小氣老婦記仇 花20年種樹遮鄰居美景","createTime":"2016-12-14T00:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T12:24:21.000Z","uid":18348,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d897e687d7e68abda28f047cfe6a569faa39eb3f","tid":38348,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:56:49.000Z","msg":"英國一名小氣老婦，因為鄰居多年前反對她加建房屋，竟然處心積慮花約20年時間，種植高達50呎的柏樹，遮擋鄰居景色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5m11F9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5m11F9D.jpg&h=e99d07ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年89歲的貝蒂（Betty Kelley）居住在英國薩默塞特郡一條郊野小村，她的屋前莊園原可以遠眺著名的Solsbury Hill的美景，誰知她和鄰近數位住戶的景色，現時已被前方的鄰居在莊園種植一列高達50呎的柏樹所遮擋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/085525_d155e4d5ec35ba7934ed0a226e90f844.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F085525_d155e4d5ec35ba7934ed0a226e90f844.jpg&h=d6eb39cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貝蒂表示，這位女鄰居在二十多年前，想加建4幢房屋，但遭她和其他鄰居反對，結果計劃胎死腹中，自此該女鄰居即開始在莊園種植柏樹，經過二十年的生長，現已變成一幅柏樹圍牆，遮擋住她們的景色，她質疑對方處心積慮實施報仇計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91VY0d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91VY0d0.jpg&h=b6d52626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地市政廳現正介入調停，希望有關鄰居以睦鄰為上，主動斬樹或將樹修剪得矮一些。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-Plastic/1635322-小氣老婦愛記仇-花20年種樹遮鄰居美景/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9-Plastic%2F1635322-%E5%B0%8F%E6%B0%A3%E8%80%81%E5%A9%A6%E6%84%9B%E8%A8%98%E4%BB%87-%E8%8A%B120%E5%B9%B4%E7%A8%AE%E6%A8%B9%E9%81%AE%E9%84%B0%E5%B1%85%E7%BE%8E%E6%99%AF%2F&d=2fXvMHh%2FMpctJjSDIpTO%2BxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=0d18c6e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-Plastic/1635322-小氣老婦愛記仇-花20年種樹遮鄰居美景/</a>"},{"pid":"24b40d45499709e090b69717e7ccf8913b316a0a","tid":38348,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e7526d58a65661adbd988934def12358c34784","tid":38348,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:58:30.000Z","msg":"君子報仇 十年未晚  既升級版"},{"pid":"442d6902248802ccb2c491bc16b3fe99b7526c65","tid":38348,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:59:59.000Z","msg":"女子報仇 廿年未晚"},{"pid":"a68170fcb5e74b7eabc01ab61accfc8242fb6314","tid":38348,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:02:48.000Z","msg":"Ho ball"},{"pid":"472cd2d498e6d45e377eac3dafae897132105a6b","tid":38348,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:04:37.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a15cef92adad51e909717adcb88dc6bc65d7ab","tid":38348,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:04:49.000Z","msg":"想問下 當初鄰居點阻止佢加建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fbf3adaa4c6d5725da5c9618e17102fbf23fa6","tid":38348,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:05:46.000Z","msg":"唔係好明<br />\n係自己地方加建房屋點解要經鄰居同意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無外國巴絲解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e79aa60d66c9383154cdcbd7d5f3e0c883b518","tid":38348,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:11:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>君子報仇 十年未晚  既升級版</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a237d882f8e22a02cdee1fbf40ff11c3b1697ee0","tid":38348,"uid":46824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0